fields.name: 3 month chocolate tasting course
fields.description:
Know someone who considers themself a bit of an epicure? A chocolate gourmet? Or simply just can’t enough chocolate? Well we’ve created the perfect club for them.
As a member of the Cocoa Runners club they’ll receive a box of four carefully selected premium chocolate bars every month in their choice of either mixed or dark bars.
With each box we aim to broaden their experiences of chocolate, from exploring single origin beans, to comparing styles and flavour from different parts of the world, to unwrapping the stories behind our artisan makers – they’ll have plenty to look forward to.
They’ll also find tasting cards and expert reviews by our team to guide them along the way. What’s more exciting than receiving the finest chocolate from around the world straight to your doorstep?!

fields.name: 3 month Colours & Flavours subscription - 2 bottles per month
fields.description: Know someone who loves wine? My Vitibox will get them from beginner to connoisseur in no time. Each month, they will receive two bottles of wine carefully selected by Alain Gousse, the former Head Sommelier of Michelin starred restaurants la Tour d’Argent, le Crillon, le Pavillon de la Rotonde and le Hameau Albert 1er. Accompanying the wine is a fun but educational booklet that walks them through how to taste each of the wines in the box, along with definitions of wine jargon to look out for and some recipe ideas to follow the key food and wine pairing rules. They can even receive small bottles of wine aromas to train their nose!

fields.name: 3 months of surprise presents
fields.description: Bored of just getting bills in the post? Well subscribe to Not-Another-Bill and each month you or your lucky recipient will receive a carefully curated & beautifully wrapped surprise present in the post. As well as making your letterbox a more magical place, our aim is to introduce subscribers to exclusive items from great artists, designers and brands. From our boxes, ribbons and beautiful tissue paper to the personalised letter explaining about the present, we really consider how the whole experience looks and feels.
